description:
The story follows Ani, a princess from the minor nation of Inako. Ani is sent to the signing ceremony that will bring peace to the rival nations of Mildonia, a mighty military country, and Selenfalen, a powerful theocracy. Ani is supposed to help steer the signing ceremony along, but she runs into trouble when she encounters a handful of obstinate princes.

(Source: Crunchyroll)

Consists of [DAIGO](https://anilist.co/staff/110119) (Vocalist, lyricist, composer), AKIHIDE (Guitarist, chorus, synthesizer, lyricist, composer, arrangement), and SHINPEI (same as AKIHIDE). There are many tied-up to their songs.

Ever since their 5th single, Everlasting Luv, they got involved into singing Detective Conan, and 10th single, CLIMBER×CLIMBER, they got involved into acting in and singing for Vanguard CMs!!
Vocalist DAIGO is popular for his grandfather being the ex-politician Noboru Takeshita. There are also some family members that are famous, including [Eiki Eiki](https://anilist.co/staff/97236), who is his older sister. He voiced in 13th Detective Conan Movie as well.

[Profile](https://www.aplus-japan.com/talent/daigo/) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/Daigo19780408) | [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/daigo_breakerz_/)

DAIGO has the vocalist of the J-Rock band [BREAKERZ](https://anilist.co/staff/111829/Breakerz) since April 2007, and was formerly the Visual Kei musician DAIGO☆STARDU
